('00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000001506', '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000105', 6, 'sentence_simplification', 'Choose the sentence that best expresses the essential meaning of this one from paragraph 4: "Critics argue that this undermines principles of justice, rights, and moral integrity."', '["Some critics think utilitarianism can support unjust or immoral acts", "Critics agree that utilitarianism protects human rights", "Utilitarianism always leads to morally correct outcomes", "Justice and rights are rarely considered by utilitarian thinkers"]', '0', 'The sentence means critics believe utilitarianism can undermine justice and moral principles.'),
